snippet.title: Spirited Thief Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Spirited Thief is a turn-based stealth game with a quirk: take your time to secretly scout and plan your heist, then break in to steal your target under increasing pressure. 

Join alpha now !

Learn more: spirited-thief.com
